race.comment: RIDE THE RIVER (6) frustrating gelding who finally gave a glimpse of what he's capable of when sticking on late to run second over 1200m at Wyong. Can spear across from the sticky gate and figure prominently. TELLING (7) returns from a 33-day let-up. Back in class when sent out favourite for a soft victory over 1300m at Orange in C1 grade. Deep into his prep and looks ready fore this tougher contest. VINDICATION (1) tough old gelding with a solid third-up record. Back in class when improved sharply for a game third over 1200m at Kembla Grange. Maps well and gets his chance.  PARIAH ENGAGEMENT (15) faded late at her first run back when sixth to Maid Of Moolah over 1300m at Hawkesbury. Can sit off them from the draw and surge late.
